Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.32,0:00:03.66,Default,Girl,0,0,0,, Do you want to walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:08.92,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,...to a place where it's warm and there are lots of fun things?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.13,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,That's what you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:13.75,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:16.78,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:52.97,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Hey Mom, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.52,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:55.08,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:01:58.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:01:59.29,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What do you play with Sanae-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:04.44,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Read books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:06.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did you bring one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:09.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How about with the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.08,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.25,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:19.87,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Komada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Imitations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:23.93,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Not funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:25.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:27.72,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:31.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is that old man teaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:36.08,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:37.88,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Come on, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.26,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:40.89,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.06,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Be quiet. You're embarrassing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:44.52,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,It's because you're not listening to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:45.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Think about those around you a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:49.37,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.52,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:51.74,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:53.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:03.51,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 18
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:03.51,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}End of the Path
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:03.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:12.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey. If you're going to the bathroom, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:14.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Were you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.75,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,She said no crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:27.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:29.24,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's unexpectedly strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.69,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,But she said there are places I can cry. {There are two places, but Ushio say only one. Leave it as plural.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.04,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:48.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess you can cry without anyone noticing in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:52.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think you can cry when you want to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's better to cry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:04:02.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There are many times when you can't cry even when you want to after you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:17.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you want a toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Choose something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:22.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll buy it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:22.90,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:32.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.05,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:48.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You would have preferred a girlier toy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:49.81,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.24,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I wanted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:52.83,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You have a strange taste, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:58.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nothing. Keep playing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:04:59.56,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's a fun summer vacation for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:08.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Of course not; not when she's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:18.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.90,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.47,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:25.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's dark, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:25.96,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.12,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I did it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.34,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's a firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You know about those, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.36,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,First time seeing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:53.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I guess those from here come out later than others. {Prime time of fireflies are June. CAS world is currently August.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.68,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:04.81,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:07.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then don't stare at other people's faces like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You have something you want to say, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:18.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What? Are you still scared of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:22.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right. Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I won't yell any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:26.49,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.97,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Tell me about Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:34.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ask Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:36.52,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,She won't tell me even if I ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She wants me to tell you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:44.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ask Sanae-san. Tell her that I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:09.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:12.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wear your hat properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:17.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We have a lot of walking today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:21.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.34,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Want to have a better look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.32,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There, spread your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:54.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wow, you're light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:55.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.95,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't run off too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:16.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I guess it was good to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.48,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:34.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.96,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:38.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Lost what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:41.76,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:46.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You didn't go any further, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:50.89,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:55.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Strange. You didn't cover much ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio, let's give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just buy the same one on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:04.08,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I want that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We can't find it, so there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:40.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a walk that way. Don't move from here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:41.67,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:51.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I know this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.51,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,You're Okazaki Tomoya-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:17.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ah... yes. You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:21.03,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Yes. I know of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:24.13,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,My name is Okazaki Shino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:25.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:30.28,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,I'm your father's, Okazaki Naoyuki's, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:39.33,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,I received a call from Furukawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.42,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,They said you'd come if I waited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Was it Sanae-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.77,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,You've really grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We've met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:54.49,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Right here, when you were still little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:59.90,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,It was after your mother, Atsuko-san, passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:06.92,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Is Naoyuki still atoning for his sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:11.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No. He should've been released and be living at home by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:13.92,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,I'm sure you experienced many emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:15.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.51,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,He was not always that foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:29.39,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Both Atsuko-san and Naoyuki were still students, so people were opposed to their marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:35.70,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,but Naoyuki quit high school and started living in a small apartment with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.96,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Regardless, it seemed he was having a great life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:44.48,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,To live protecting the one he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:48.00,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,That's all it took to make him happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:53.49,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Soon, Atsuko-san was pregnant with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:59.63,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,and you were born, treasured by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:08.84,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,But the happy life didn't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.32,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Atsuko-san passed away in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:20.12,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,To him, it was an event too sad to recover from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:27.95,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,But he couldn't let himself fall into the depths of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:34.91,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Tomoya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:39.17,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,He still had you to care for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:44.04,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,He said he would raise you to be a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:52.77,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,That day, you walked away from here holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:55.18,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:13:01.65,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,The days after that were the days he worked the hardest in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:06.57,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,He was fired from many jobs and went from one place to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:10.45,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Even then, he worked with you in his care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:16.08,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,He would buy you toys with\Nthe little money he had and give you snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:22.13,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,He sacrificed all his luck and chances for success.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:28.51,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,At times, he might have been strict or violent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:33.71,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,but it was all to raise you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:41.86,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,However, for Naoyuki, it was a very hard life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:46.61,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,To relieve the pain from work, he indulged in alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.92,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,I heard there were times he was drunk and out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:56.45,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Even so, he chose to live with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:07.98,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,And, by the time you had grown and could choose your own path, Naoyuki had lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:13.60,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Work, faith, luck, friends. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:19.73,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,I heard you're in a situation similar to his right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.57,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,It is a painful situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:28.92,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,But that's why I wanted let you hear this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:33.14,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,I wanted you to know what kind of father Naoyuki was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He often bought me snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:43.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Also, going on walks, holding hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why did I forget all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:53.27,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Tomoya-san. Do you think Naoyuki was a bad father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:55.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm an even worse man than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:04.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm standing at the same place Pops stood that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:08.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yet I'm weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:10.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.21,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,So is he.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:18.67,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,He's weak, pathetic, and clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:24.54,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Still, he did his best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:30.67,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,I want to hold him as my pride and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:34.25,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,He had many failures as a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:38.47,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,but I believe that he was a fine father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:40.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:47.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.31,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:56.82,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,I feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:08.42,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Tomoya-san. He tried too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.00,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,It's about time he can rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:17.51,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,Can you tell Naoyuki to come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:23.02,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,I will be waiting for him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:31.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.44,Default,Gra,0,0,0,,That's your child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yes. She's Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've been searching all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.07,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:51.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:01.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:06.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We might not be able to find that robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:07.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So let's buy another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:18.23,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,There's only one. {As in it's unique}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There were lots of them at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:26.79,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,It's the one you chose and bought for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:32.50,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,First thing from Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:39.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Were you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:44.03,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:48.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Was it fun to come on a trip with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.22,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:52.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:58.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio... would it be all right if I stayed with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:03.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I've been a bad daddy for many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:08.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,but I'll do my best for you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:12.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So, would it be all right if I stayed with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:14.29,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:15.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.64,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,I want you to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:25.83,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,But today, I lost an important thing, so I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:28.95,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.27,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:42.26,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Is it all right not to hold it in anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.99,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Sanae-san told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.88,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Places I can cry are in the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:54.47,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,...and in Daddy's arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:58.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:00.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:19.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:22.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:26.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you want to hear about Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.44,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:49.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right. Then come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:19:59.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:06.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mommy was a crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:11.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even the first time we met.\NShe wasn't sure of herself and was weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:14.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She stood still at the foot of the hill to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Guess what she said at the foot of the hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:22.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She closed her eyes and said, "Sweet bean bread."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That was Mommy's habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Saying out loud something she wanted to eat to gather her courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:36.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san was really busy at that time\Nand didn't have the time to make Mommy's bento.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:42.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maybe she could have if she'd tried,\Nbut Mommy said not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:45.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's what Mommy was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ah... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:58.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mommy was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:07.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:09.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:15.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:21.44,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:25.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are you crying, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:31.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry. I was remembering Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:39.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right, let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:44.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mommy wanted to do theater at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:46.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you know what theater is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa. I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:53.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Something only I can protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:58.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The precious thing only I can protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:05.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was...
