Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:37.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,...right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:44.10,Default,2,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:45.85,San,San,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:50.86,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,A guy that used to have eyes of a dead fish is up and about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:53.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You like the Big Dango Family, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.97,0:23:58.03,Ush,Ush,0,0,0,,Sanae-san said this is how Mommy smelled.
